%% 3.1.8 Student Roster — sequence (layered)
%% Actor > UI > Controller > Service > Repository > Database

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Actor as Admin
    participant UI as UI (/students-roster)
    participant SC as Controller (StudentController)
    participant SS as Service (StudentService)
    participant Repo as Repository (IRepository Student)
    participant DB as Database (SQL Server)

    Actor->>UI: Open Student Roster
    UI->>SC: GET /api/Student/Search (keyword, campusId, status, paging)
    SC->>SS: SearchStudentAsync
    SS->>Repo: Query students + Guardian + Campus
    Repo->>DB: SELECT
    DB-->>Repo: rows
    SS-->>SC: PagedResult StudentDto
    SC-->>UI: 200 — grid

    Actor->>UI: Filter by Campus — e.g. Thu Duc
    UI->>SC: GET /api/Student/Search?campusId=...&...
    SC->>SS: SearchStudentAsync
    SS->>Repo: Filter by CampusId
    Repo->>DB: SELECT
    SS-->>SC: filtered page
    SC-->>UI: 200 — table updates (transition animation FE)

    Note over UI,SC: Filter by Route / Classroom — client-side hoặc tham số mở rộng nếu backend bổ sung.

    Actor->>UI: Double-click row or View — Nguyen Van B
    UI->>UI: Router push → Child Analysis / student detail

    UI->>SC: GET /api/Student/Get/{id}
    SC->>SS: GetStudentByIdAsync(id)
    SS->>Repo: Include Guardian, Campus
    Repo->>DB: SELECT
    SS-->>SC: StudentDto
    SC-->>UI: 200 — profile + guardian

    opt Recent boarding / face history
        UI->>UI: GET Attendance or logs by studentId (AttendanceController / FaceRecognition logs as designed)
    end

    Note over Actor,DB: BR08 — trên màn chi tiết: Admin cập nhật trạng thái học sinh (ví dụ DISABLED) qua PUT /api/Student/Update/{id} (StudentUpdateDto.Status).
